oving6.stringgrid

Interface StringGrid

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    StringGridImpl

    public interface StringGrid
extends java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.String>
    An interface with methods for managing the content of a String grid. The grid has a number of rows (the grid's height) and columns (the grid's width). In each cell in the grid there is a String that can be set with the setElement method and read with the getElement method.
